{"word":"H1709 - דָּג - dâg - dawg - Fish","slug":"H1709","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">דָּג</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>dâg"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dawg"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fish"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05D0;&#x05D2;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05D2;</b><sup></bdo>o</sup> - <b>da&#x0302;<a href='S:g'>g</a>  da&#x0302;'g</b> - <i>dawg,</i>  <i>dawg</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1711\">H1711</a>; a fish (as <i>prolific</i>); or perhaps rather from <a href=\"#/H1672\">H1672</a> (as <i>timid</i>); but still better from <a href=\"#/H1672\">H1672</a> (in the sense of <i>squirming</i>, that is, moving by the vibratory action of the tail); a <i>fish</i> (often used collectively): - fish."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1710\">H1710</a>, <a href=\"#/H1711\">H1711</a>, <a href=\"#/H1712\">H1712</a>, <a href=\"#/H1728\">H1728</a>, <a href=\"#/H1729\">H1729</a>, <a href=\"#/H1770\">H1770</a>, <a href=\"#/H1771\">H1771</a>"}]}